  "text": "It is important to mention that both PCR and qPCR can be used in the analysis of peripheral blood samples and also in several host tissues (biopsy or euthanized experimental animals) and therefore represent an important contribution in the parasitological cure monitoring of animals and humans hosts [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
